---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 423
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=Deviation
By: Muhammad ibnu l'Munawwar
---
If any one by means of asceticism and self-mortification shall have
risen to an exalted degree of mystical experience, without having a
Pir to whose authority and example he submits himself, the Sûfîs do
not regard him as belonging to their community.
